{"tid":935074,"cid":21,"subCid":1,"title":"[太叻啦]陳柏宇同iu合唱韓文歌《잔소리 (Nagging)》","createTime":"2018-12-09T17:40:47.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-13T03:58:08.000Z","uid":181093,"like":22,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"2af111a2278048822fbb1e5c6afc0edf6487ce41","tid":935074,"uid":181093,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T17:40:47.000Z","msg":"只係學左幾個月，啲韓文發音已經練到咁準仲唱到出黎<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n片：<br />\n<a href=\"https://youtu.be/HQ9XdZHamb4\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FHQ9XdZHamb4&d=kph3hhp6ZJ7xbSYcTQLF8gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=04f895e2\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/HQ9XdZHamb4</a><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/4yunc2H.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F4yunc2H.png&h=d91cc4a0&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/qHAYvPs.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FqHAYvPs.png&h=bb2296d7&s={SIZE}\" /><img src=\"https://na.cx/i/BStSAf7.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FBStSAf7.png&h=2bad1b5f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n第一次覺得韓文歌咁好聽❤️❤️❤️❤️"},{"pid":"e450be6f53cd0e9ad785c01570cd5884b18acb54","tid":935074,"uid":3032,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T17:46:12.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6d845c4ef3e88cd2e6164b070e1156a43b76e28e","tid":935074,"uid":181093,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-09T17:47:56.000Z","msg":"韓國靚聲女歌手IU昨晚假亞洲國際博覽館舉行出道10周年演唱會，全晚唱出《Good Day》、《Twenty-three》、《Palette》及《Only I didn&lsquo;t know》等多首經典歌曲，亦唱出紀念出道10周年的歌曲《BBIBBI》，而昨晚更請來韓國男歌手Sam Kim及香港男歌手陳柏宇（Jason）擔任嘉賓，令粉絲十分驚喜。 <br />\n<br />\n而IU又與Jason合唱韓文歌《Nagging》，IU大讚對方的韓文發音好，叫全場為他鼓掌，Jason指11年前曾在銅鑼灣唱日文歌，今次是第二次挑戰唱外語歌，相隔10年覺得背外語很難，幸好有老師細心教他，而他又唱出廣東歌《霸氣情歌》及《後排慶功宴》。 <br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181209/mobile/bkn-20181209113825944-1209_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20181209%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20181209113825944-1209_00862_001.html&d=kph3hhp6ZJ7xbSYcTQLF8gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=7440fffd\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20181209/mobile/bkn-20181209113825944-1209_00862_001.html</a>"},{"pid":"3e1a585ec1025f4c945e348a3160b66f358f5509","tid":935074,"uid":1130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:16:48.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://youtu.be/LDOnkfXbXYk\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FLDOnkfXbXYk&d=kph3hhp6ZJ7xbSYcTQLF8gHuyxefasl%2FZxVLfhQSBMM%3D&h=6274b1ce\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/LDOnkfXbXYk</a><br />\n講嘢果度好笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2032c36fe9ca8b2baf7abfd704833c84116949d6","tid":935074,"uid":555,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T16:19:01.000Z","msg":"IU❤"},{"pid":"70736df79d5a686bce52531ac83c7fe1cad13e28","tid":935074,"uid":112303,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T17:17:23.000Z","msg":"見過陳柏宇真人得米67,8<br />\nIu 高踭鞋都仲矮過佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4457c6de072fcb77e7c8912c76ef4a3fbe1f3aee","tid":935074,"uid":20286,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-10T17:21:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d47bf18998240bb816f6c9073aa4f65a116a18e","tid":935074,"uid":181093,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"3e1a585ec1025f4c945e348a3160b66f358f5509","tid":935074,"uid":1130,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"repl